timelineItems.desc: A high-profile match in the Eastern Conference is ahead on Saturday evening when D.C. United play host to Toronto FC on Saturday evening at RFK Stadium.
timelineItems.title: KICKOFF: D.C. United vs Toronto FC | June 6, 2015

timelineItems.text: Do #TFC even know Steven Birnbaum is on the field? Unbelievably poor marking of one of #DCU's primary threats on set pieces. #DCU

timelineItems.name: Toronto FC
timelineItems.text: 18' Reds playing with fire. Free kick D.C. in a dangerous spot. #TFCLive
